# React hooks are auto-imported

This project uses `unplugin-auto-import`, so **do not write**:

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
import { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from "react";
```

Instead, just use hooks directly:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
function Example() {
  const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
  useEffect(() => {}, []);
  return <div>{count}</div>;
}
```

